{"nodes": [{"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_05_banco_nuvem_firebase_design_banco_nuvem_firebase", "label": "Banco na nuvem (Firebase Auth + Firestore)", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-05-banco-nuvem-firebase-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Troca localStorage por nuvem 24/7 gr\u00e1tis (plano Spark, n\u00e3o pausa), login de qualquer aparelho, tempo real. Site continua est\u00e1tico na Vercel, vanilla JS sem bundler (SDK modular via CDN). YAGNI expl\u00edcito: sem partilha de obras, sem normalizar em cole\u00e7\u00f5es por gasto."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_05_banco_nuvem_firebase_design_documento_dados_uid", "label": "Documento dados/{uid} (blob \u00fanico por usu\u00e1rio)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-05-banco-nuvem-firebase-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Um documento Firestore por usu\u00e1rio com o mesmo objeto JSON do localStorage ({obras:[], config:{...}}); 1 MB \u2248 d\u00e9cadas de gastos, aceit\u00e1vel. Conflito: \u00faltima escrita vence (blob inteiro) \u2014 aceit\u00e1vel porque \u00e9 usu\u00e1rio \u00fanico por conta, multi-aparelho. Escrita com debounce ~300 ms."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_05_banco_nuvem_firebase_design_firebase_auth_email_senha", "label": "Login e-mail + senha (Firebase Auth)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-05-banco-nuvem-firebase-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "CPF deixa de ser credencial e vira campo do perfil (perfis/{uid}). 'Esqueci minha senha' por e-mail. Sem migra\u00e7\u00e3o autom\u00e1tica de senhas antigas: recadastro manual, poucos usu\u00e1rios."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_05_banco_nuvem_firebase_design_sincronizacao_tempo_real", "label": "Sincroniza\u00e7\u00e3o em tempo real (onSnapshot)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-05-banco-nuvem-firebase-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "onSnapshot no documento do usu\u00e1rio; mudan\u00e7a vinda de outro aparelho atualiza db e chama renderAll(). Eco da pr\u00f3pria escrita ignorado via hasPendingWrites."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_05_banco_nuvem_firebase_design_persistencia_offline_firestore", "label": "Persist\u00eancia offline do Firestore (persistentLocalCache)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-05-banco-nuvem-firebase-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "PWA abre e lan\u00e7a gastos sem internet; sincroniza ao reconectar; Firestore re-tenta grava\u00e7\u00f5es sozinho (fila offline). Limite: primeiro login de um aparelho exige internet."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_05_banco_nuvem_firebase_design_migracao_dados_locais", "label": "Migra\u00e7\u00e3o de dados locais antigos", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-05-banco-nuvem-firebase-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "No primeiro login em aparelho com blob local (obras_data_v1::CPF): se a nuvem est\u00e1 vazia, oferece importar; flag local evita perguntar de novo. Nunca sobrescreve nuvem que j\u00e1 tem obras."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_05_banco_nuvem_firebase_design_firestore_rules", "label": "Firestore security rules (uid == uid)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-05-banco-nuvem-firebase-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "allow read, write apenas se request.auth.uid == uid, em dados/{uid} e perfis/{uid}. Chaves do firebaseConfig s\u00e3o p\u00fablicas \u2014 a seguran\u00e7a vem das rules."}, {"id": "cloud_savedados", "label": "saveDados(blob) (cloud.js)", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-05-banco-nuvem-firebase-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "cloud_watchdados", "label": "watchDados(cb) (cloud.js)", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-05-banco-nuvem-firebase-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}], "edges": [{"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_05_banco_nuvem_firebase_design_banco_nuvem_firebase", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_05_banco_nuvem_firebase_design_documento_dados_uid", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-05-banco-nuvem-firebase-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_05_banco_nuvem_firebase_design_banco_nuvem_firebase", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_05_banco_nuvem_firebase_design_firebase_auth_email_senha", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-05-banco-nuvem-firebase-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_05_banco_nuvem_firebase_design_banco_nuvem_firebase", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_05_banco_nuvem_firebase_design_sincronizacao_tempo_real", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-05-banco-nuvem-firebase-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superp